text: Walnut Bread () is a 1978 Lithuanian drama movie directed by Arūnas Žebriūnas and starring Algirdas Latėnas, Saulius Sipaitis, Doloresa Kazragytė, Leonid Obolensky, Antanas Šurna. ==Other websites== * Category:1978 drama movies Category:Lithuanian movies Category:Movies set in Lithuania
